OL,3,CFarage to launch his party's local
OL,4,Celection campaign in Sunderland
OL,6,FNigel Farage will officially launch
OL,7,FReform UK's local election campaign in
OL,8,FSunderland on Thursday evening (26
OL,9,FMarch), promising to deliver "a breath
OL,10,Fof fresh air in English councils up
OL,11,Fand down the UK".
OL,13,FThe Reform leader has held a series of
OL,14,Felection rallies across the country in
OL,15,Frecent weeks, but will formally begin
OL,16,Fhis party's campaign for the May 7
OL,17,Fpolls at the event at the Sunderland
OL,18,FLive Arena in Houghton-le-Spring.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/6
