CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1774890348
OL,3,CFarage to launch his party's local
OL,4,Celection campaign in Sunderland
OL,6,FHe is expected to use the event to
OL,7,Flist a series of achievements in the
OL,8,Flocal authorities already run by
OL,9,FReform, such as Durham County Council,
OL,10,Fsaying voters are "already seeing a
OL,11,Fdifference on the ground".
OL,13,FAhead of the rally, Mr Farage said
OL,14,FReform was "delivering a total culture
OL,15,Fshift in local government, sweeping
OL,16,Faway the establishment consensus and
OL,17,Ffinally putting residents first".
OL,26,@rD@SOUsD@YO]vD@LOUyD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
