PN,42903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1774890348
OL,3,CFarage to launch his party's local
OL,4,Celection campaign in Sunderland
OL,6,FHe added: "Where the old parties have
OL,7,Ffailed and left behind a trail of
OL,8,Fruined councils in their wake, Reform
OL,9,Fwill deliver a breath of fresh air in
OL,10,FEnglish councils up and down the UK."
OL,12,FCentral to his pitch will be Reform's
OL,13,Fclaim to have identified #700 million
OL,14,Fin savings across its 12 councils,
OL,15,Fwhich Mr Farage claimed had been
OL,16,Fdelivered "without touching frontline
OL,17,Fservices".
OL,19,FIn November last year, Reform said its
OL,20,Fcouncils had saved #331 million.
OL,26,@nD@KOUrD@eO]xD@KOUyD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/6
