CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1774890348
OL,3,CFarage to launch his party's local
OL,4,Celection campaign in Sunderland
OL,6,FReform continues to lead in the polls
OL,7,Fand is expected to do well in May,
OL,8,Fadding to the 677 councillors it won
OL,9,Fin last year's local elections.
OL,11,FBut the significant savings the party
OL,12,Fclaims to have made have been disputed
OL,13,Fby opposition councillors, while
OL,14,FLabour has pointed to care homes and
OL,15,Fadult education services closing in
OL,16,FReform-run Derbyshire.
OL,18,FLabour has also criticised Reform for
OL,19,Fincreasing council tax despite
OL,20,Fpromising to cut the levy before last
OL,21,Fyear's local elections.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
