PN,42905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1774890348
OL,3,CFarage to launch his party's local
OL,4,Celection campaign in Sunderland
OL,6,FReform now says council tax rises in
OL,7,Fauthorities where it has majority
OL,8,Fcontrol have averaged less than those
OL,9,Frun by Labour, the Conservatives or
OL,10,Fthe Lib Dems, while describing below-
OL,11,Finflation increases in some councils
OL,12,Fas a "real-terms tax cut".
OL,14,FBut this does not include
OL,15,FWorcestershire, where Reform runs a
OL,16,Fminority administration and increased
OL,17,Fcouncil tax this year by 9%.
OL,19,FLabour Party chairwoman Anna Turley
OL,20,Fsaid: "Reform's promises fall apart
OL,21,Fthe moment they take power.
OL,26,@tD@FOUtD@YO]|D@GOU
