OL,3,CFarage to launch his party's local
OL,4,Celection campaign in Sunderland
OL,6,F"They said they would cut taxes and
OL,7,Fwaste, but in council after council
OL,8,Fthey're hiking council tax and
OL,9,Fslashing services."
